Install dependencies
-------
For UNIX / Linux, simply enter the following command that will install all necessary packages:

(Debian, Fedora)
% sudo apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev imagemagick

(Vine)
% sudo apt-get install freeglut freeglut-devel imagemagick

(RedHat, Fedora)
% sudo yum install freeglut
% sudo yum install freeglut-devel
% sudo yum install imagemagick

Compile
-------
./compile.py

Usage
-------
./stl2gif -i [input-file] [OPTIONS]

Options
-------

-h : Print help message

-i : STL infile path (MANDATORY)

-o : GIF outfile name

-s : Set zoom factor. Default is 2.5

-w : Render in wiremesh mode. Default is filled polygons

-x : Set X axis rotation speed. Default is 0.0

-y : Set Y axis rotation speed. Default is 0.0

-z : Set Z axis rotation speed. Default is 5.0
